    <div class="Activity.name">Math Talk: A Whole Number and a Unit Fraction</div>
    <div class="im_statement"><p>Decide mentally whether each statement is true.</p>

<ul>
	<li><span class="math">\(\frac15 \boldcdot 45 = \frac{45}{5}\)</span></li>
	<li><span class="math">\(\frac15 \boldcdot 20 = \frac14 \boldcdot 24\)</span></li>
	<li><span class="math">\(42 \boldcdot \frac16 = \frac16 \boldcdot 42\)</span></li>
	<li><span class="math">\(486 \boldcdot \frac{1}{12} = \frac{480}{12}+\frac{6}{12}\)</span></li>
</ul>
</div>
